                                67' Antognoni rig., 89' Desolati
Juventus - Inter        2-0     32' Bettega, 79' Fanna
Milan - Torino          0-2     31' Zaccarelli, 79' Pulici
Pescara - Lazio         2-0     50' Prestanti, 76' Chinellato  
Roma - Perugia          4-0     26' aut. Dal Fiume, 46' Benetti,
                                61' Pruzzo rig., 86' Ancelotti            
Udinese - Napoli        0-0
Classifica - Inter 34; Juventus e Roma 28; Ascoli, Avellino, Fiorentina,
             Milan e Torino 26; Perugia 25; Bologna e Cagliari 24; Napoli 23;
             Lazio 21; Catanzaro 18; Udinese 16; Pescara 13.  

At the end of the matches, in the stadiums of Roma, Milano, Pescara, Avellino,
Palermo and Genova many players and executives were arrested (e.g. the president
of Milan, Colombo, and the players Albertosi, Giordano, Wilson, Paolo Rossi, 
Cacciatori and Manfredonia) because of the Totonero scandal.

